Library common files
--------------------

This folder contains basic libraries

power_monitor.h/cpp:	
--------------------

The power monitor of the library, with database for event recording and analysis engine.
Power monitoring can be separately enabled for every IP of the library, by setting the 'pow_mon' constructor parameter.

timingmonitor.h/cpp:
--------------------

Class with static functions for tracking SystemC time and real execution time of tests.
Used by most of the unit tests.

vendian.h / msb_lsb.h
---------------------

Functions for endianess conversion - depending on host system.

socrocket.h
-----------

Collection of important header files. Meant to ease extension of the library.

vendian.h
---------

Implementation of verbosity levels for the library.
Used by all IPs and most testbenches.


ahbdevice.cpp/h
---------------

implement an ahb device interface

ahbmaster.tpp/h
---------------

provide an ahb master interface

ahbslave.tpp/h
--------------

provide an ahb slave interface

apbdevice.tpp/h
---------------

clkdevice.cpp/h
---------------

implement a clock device

memdevice.cpp/h
---------------

implement a basic memory device

strace.cpp
----------

wscript
-------

waf build file



